WLC_POINTER_GET_POSITION(3)                                   WLC API FUNCITONS

NAME

    wlc_pointer_get_position - gets the mouse pointer position

SYNOPSIS

    void wlc_pointer_get_position(const struct wlc_point *out_position);

DESCRIPTION

    wlc_pointer_get_position() is used to get the mouse pointer position on the
    currently focused output.

RETURN VALUE

    None.
